Our new Premium Economy seats are making a debut at Arabian Travel Market 2021. The highly-anticipated seat will be on display at the Emirates stand for visitors to experience from 16 to 19 May.
 
In addition, we will also showcase our most popular onboard products, including our:

✈️ @Boeing 777-300ER gamechanger fully enclosed First Class private suite
✈️ @Boeing 777-300ER Business Class seat
✈️ Refreshed @Airbus A380 Onboard lounge and others
 
#FlyEmiratesFlyBetter #EmiratesAirline #ATMDubai @arabian_travel_market
